# Fence VisitAPI dialogue - cinematic text lens version
# In raid: use accept/handover/complete.
# Out of raid: Talk can jump to @tasks.
# DLG is treated as a text camera: scene, object, pause, NPC intent, player choice.

trader: 579dc571d53a0658a154fbec "Fence"
start: root
quest proof = 69f1ce000000000000000001
quest alive_price = 69f1ce000000000000000002
trigger: raid bigmap (310.1499, -1.9962151, -175.2366) dist 3 radius 1.2 repeat "Talk to Fence"

<root> bg: FenceBackGround.png
The room is too quiet. / 房间很安静。安静得过分。

An old casing shifts at the corner of the table. / 桌角有一枚旧弹壳，微微滚动了一下。

Fence does not look up. / Fence 没有抬头。

"You came." / “你来了。”

A pause. / 停顿。

"That still tells me nothing." / “这还说明不了什么。”
- You said you had work. / 你说过有活。 -> proof
- You said I still owed you. / 你说过我还欠你。 -> alive_price
# Shared root: @tasks is only meaningful when this dialogue is opened from the out-of-raid Talk button.
- Show me your tasks. / 给我看看你的任务。 -> @tasks
- I'm leaving. / 我走了。 -> @close

<proof> bg: FenceBackGround.png
The room is too quiet. / 房间很安静。安静得过分。

A strip of cloth lies on the table. Fence presses it down hard with one finger. / 桌上只放着一条折过的布条。Fence 用一根手指死死压着它。

"A tag." / “狗牌。”

He mentions neither USEC nor BEAR. / 他没有提 USEC，也没有提 BEAR。

"Metal remembers better than men." / “金属比人记得牢。”
- Why a dogtag? / 为什么是狗牌？ -> proof_question
- You are buying names. / 你在买名字。 -> proof_names
- [USEC] You knew what I was before I woke up. / [USEC] 我醒来之前，你就知道我是什么人。 -> proof_usec
- Fine. I'll bring you one. / 行，我去带一枚回来。 -> root | accept: proof
- Here's your tag. / 狗牌带来了。 -> root | handover: proof
- That's your proof. Pay up. / 证明给你了，付钱。 -> root | complete: proof
# Only useful out of raid. In raid this option no-ops by VisitAPI design.
- Show me your tasks. / 给我看看你的任务。 -> @tasks
- Not now. / 现在不谈。 -> @close

<proof_question> bg: FenceBackGround.png
Fence turns the cloth over. The other side is blank. / Fence 把布条翻了一面。另一面空空如也。

"Because a mouth lies." / “因为嘴会撒谎。”

He taps the table once. The sound is dull. / 他敲了一下桌面，声音很闷。

"A tag only says someone stopped moving." / “狗牌只说明有人停下了。”

A pause. / 停顿。

"Bring one back." / “带一枚回来。”
- Fine. I'll bring you one. / 行，我去带一枚回来。 -> root | accept: proof
- You are buying names. / 你在买名字。 -> proof_names
- Not now. / 现在不谈。 -> @close

<proof_names> bg: FenceBackGround.png
Fence almost smiles. Almost. / Fence 像是笑了一下。也只是像。

"Names are cheap." / “名字很便宜。”

He slides an empty casing toward you. / 他把一枚空弹壳推到你面前。

"What I buy is the silence after them." / “我买的是名字后面的安静。”
- What does that mean? / 这是什么意思？ -> proof_cutoff
- Fine. I'll bring you one. / 行，我去带一枚回来。 -> root | accept: proof
- Not now. / 现在不谈。 -> @close

<proof_usec> bg: FenceBackGround.png
The room loses a little air. / 房间里的空气像是少了一点。

Fence's hand stops on the cloth. / Fence 的手停在那条布上。

"You still say that word like it belongs to you." / “你现在还把那个词说得像是属于你。”

He looks up at last. / 他终于抬眼。

"Bring a tag. Any side." / “带一枚狗牌。哪边都行。”
- Any side? / 哪边都行？ -> proof_side
- Fine. I'll bring you one. / 行，我去带一枚回来。 -> root | accept: proof
- Not now. / 现在不谈。 -> @close

<proof_side> bg: FenceBackGround.png
"USEC. BEAR." / “USEC。BEAR。”

Fence folds the cloth again. Neater this time. / Fence 又把布条折好。这一次更整齐。

"The ground does not care which patch they wore." / “地面不在乎他们戴哪块臂章。”
- Fine. I'll bring you one. / 行，我去带一枚回来。 -> root | accept: proof
- Not now. / 现在不谈。 -> @close

<proof_cutoff> bg: FenceBackGround.png
Fence pushes the casing back into the dark with one finger. / Fence 用一根手指把弹壳推回阴影里。

"It means you heard the price." / “意思是你听见价了。”

"One tag." / “一枚狗牌。”
- Fine. I'll bring you one. / 行，我去带一枚回来。 -> root | accept: proof
- Not now. / 现在不谈。 -> @close

<alive_price> bg: FenceBackGround.png
Fence does not look at you first. / Fence 没有先看你。

The dogtag lies under his fingers. He turns it slowly. The chain scrapes across the table, sharp. / 狗牌压在他的指下。他慢慢把它翻了一面，链子刮过桌面，声音刺耳。

"Customs." / “海关。”

An old folded map lies by his hand, corner blackened. / 旧地图躺在他手边，角落发黑。

"You know that road." / “你认识那条路。”

The room falls quiet for a moment. / 房间安静了一会儿。

"Maybe it remembers you too." / “也许它也还记得你。”
- What are you testing? / 你到底想试什么？ -> alive_price_question
- You know where I woke up. / 你知道我在哪里醒来的。 -> alive_price_oldgas
- I'll clear the road. / 我会把路清出来。 -> root | accept: alive_price
- The road is clear. / 路清了。 -> root | complete: alive_price
# Only useful out of raid. In raid this option no-ops by VisitAPI design.
- Show me your tasks. / 给我看看你的任务。 -> @tasks
- Not now. / 现在不谈。 -> @close

<alive_price_question> bg: FenceBackGround.png
Fence's mouth twitches, but he doesn't smile. / Fence 嘴角微微一动，却没有笑出来。

He taps the dogtag once with his fingertip. / 他用指尖敲了一下狗牌。

"This only says someone else died." / “这只能说明别人死了。”

He looks at your hands, not your face. / 他盯着你的手，而不是脸。

"It says nothing about you." / “说明不了你。”
- I'll clear the road. / 我会把路清出来。 -> root | accept: alive_price
- You know where I woke up. / 你知道我在哪里醒来的。 -> alive_price_oldgas
- Not now. / 现在不谈。 -> @close

<alive_price_oldgas> bg: FenceBackGround.png
The air in the room grows heavy. / 房间里的空气忽然沉了下去。

Fence's fingers freeze on the map. / Fence 的手指停在地图上，一动不动。

Old Gas is heavily circled in black. No label. / 旧加油站被黑笔重重圈住。没有一个字的标注。

He folds the map before you can see more. / 在你看清楚之前，他迅速把地图折起。

"Customs." / “海关。”
- What did you see there? / 你在那里看见了什么？ -> alive_price_cutoff
- I'll go. / 我去。 -> root | accept: alive_price
- Not now. / 现在不谈。 -> @close

<alive_price_cutoff> bg: FenceBackGround.png
Fence looks past you toward the board behind him. / Fence 的视线越过你，落在身后的情报板上。

For a moment, his fingers grip the edge of the table tightly, knuckles white. / 一瞬间，他的手指死死扣住桌沿，指节发白。

Then he releases it. / 随后松开。

"Five Scavs." / “五个 Scav。”

"Come back breathing." / “活着回来。”
- I'll clear the road. / 我会把路清出来。 -> root | accept: alive_price
- Not now. / 现在不谈。 -> @close

